SUMMARY:New Jersey Restaurant & Hospitality Association: ServSafe Food Saf
 ety Manager Course & Exam
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260504T090000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260504T170000
UID:89ebbc7bfbe8eb2e52d7344014303f1a@growthzone.com
DESCRIPTION:ServSafe Food Safety Manager Training and Certification is req
 uired by law in the state of New Jersey. Currently\, the state law require
 s that at least one person per establishment be ServSafe Food Safety Manag
 er-certified. Classes are taught in one day—you take both the class and 
 the exam in the same day.The class will run from 9am to 5pm with a break f
 or lunch. Be sure to arrive on time with a #2 pencil and a photo ID. You w
 ill need a 70% or above in order to pass the test. Since ServSafe is now o
 ffering electronic certificates\, please ensure that you provide a valid e
 mail address on the answer sheet. You will receive your certificate via em
 ail within 2-3 weeks. Some important notes: You must be logged into your N
 JRHA member portal to receive the member discount. Please contact saritac@
 njrha.org or info@njrha.org if you need help accessing the portal or don't
  know your login credentials.The "promo code" field on the NJRHA registrat
 ion page is how they allow you to pay to retest. This 
URL:https://business.northessexchamber.com/events/details/new-jersey-resta
 urant-hospitality-association-servsafe-food-safety-manager-course-exam
X-SOURCE:North Essex Chamber of Commerce
END:VEVENT
